data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on a sprawling one-acre lot, where country charm meets modern comfort. This 1672 square foot residence offers a perfect blend of functionality and style, featuring 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a bonus room for added flexibility. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of an open living, dining, and kitchen area. The seamless flow of laminate flooring throughout creates a cozy atmosphere, while the wood look tile in wet areas adds a touch of rustic elegance. This home is designed for those who appreciate custom finishes that exude country charm. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, where culinary delights come to life. Imagine preparing meals in this space adorned with modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient layout that makes cooking a joy. The open design ensures that the chef is always part of the conversation, whether entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. The master bedroom is a true retreat, boasting a spacious layout and an en-suite bathroom that defines luxury. Pamper yourself in the master bathroom featuring a walk-in shower and a tub with dual shower heads, creating a spa-like experience right at home. This private oasis is the perfect escape after a long day. The second bedroom once was 2 bedrooms and can easily be transitioned back with the addition of a wall. Currently the room offers a ton of space with its 20 x 12 dimensions and closet that spans the length of room. The additional bonus room can be tailored to suit your needs – whether it's a home office, a playroom, or a cozy reading nook. One of the standout features of this home is the large laundry/mudroom, providing functionality and convenience. With access to the covered carport, unloading groceries becomes less stressful and your home becomes less messy. The metal roof adds durability and a touch of character to the exterior, ensuring that your home stands the test of time. Situated on a generous one-acre lot, the possibilities for outdoor enjoyment are endless. Create your own oasis, whether it's a lush garden, a play area for kids, or a space for entertaining under the open sky. This home is more than just a residence; it's a reflection of your lifestyle. With thoughtful design, quality finishes, and a touch of country charm, every corner of this property invites you to create lasting memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this dream home yours – schedule a viewing today and experience the magic for yourself.
